<item>
            <title>[FLINK-7102] improve ClassLoaderITCase</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-7102</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt&gt;ClassLoaderITCase&lt;/tt&gt;...&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;unnecessarily runs multiple tests in a single test case&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;tt&gt;#testDisposeSavepointWithCustomKvState()&lt;/tt&gt; does not cancel its job (thus the order of execution of test cases defines the outcome)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;uses &lt;tt&gt;e.getCause().getCause()&lt;/tt&gt; which may cause {{NullPointerException}}s hiding the original error&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
